## ⚠️ Troubleshooting

| Issue | Solution |
|-------|----------|
| `python` not recognized | Use `python3` instead, or add Python to PATH |
| Module not found errors | Make sure venv is activated: `.venv\Scripts\activate` |
| WHOIS timeout | Some domains block WHOIS; this is handled gracefully |
| SSL connection errors | Normal for non-HTTPS sites; flagged as suspicious |
| Unicode display issues | Already fixed in code — should work on all Windows terminals |

